{"type": "article", "id": 58675, "title": "肯德基“圣诞炸鸡店”开始营业，可口可乐办了个艺术展宣传反家暴 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-11-26T04:55:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 64, "name": "广告"}, {"id": 873, "name": "星巴克"}, {"id": 5993, "name": "李宁"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 56, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181126122626Ik0v1bLRHEJ37uQO.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p>FILA 在福州东百中心开了国内第一家全品类门店，还同时宣布<b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4309631419288609?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">黄景瑜成为 FILA 时尚运动代言人。</a></b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126122822yu85leJLpdCamoTR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500585\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"8tju\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjg4Mzg5ODA0MA==&amp;mid=2656250179&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=e76514e04f02ccf684bc7b127907caa1&amp;chksm=987cb494af0b3d82660681a48db24d1a09734c02831c4618dbe3f8096484badc2d6c567ddfb5&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1126xUH2DEMoyfsTvIMxhwmK&amp;key=b97634afb8bc8a87fa695963622f6f2b8704b119091e5b7a31ad7d98abdb0e4cca0601d7ae2224647ddc9baed2ec037715efab004a30638285283d5f3cb80a493527d94f3d503242bf54a1621b4700ad&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=ndY%2BOU0xNU02rGMjNbZzV1FVul9mBnD9fBd5bPMjNkav28g20f1zyvez5dav68jd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>星巴克联合 Herschel Supply 推出新系列，</b></a>包括星杯、背包、手提袋，还有星礼卡。将于 12 月 5 日上市。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811261228079cDOYHbIdjJmpTe4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.526154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"pzsa\">同时星巴克的“圣诞奇梦倒数日历”将于 12 月 1 日起发售，用 24 件星巴克周边产品迎接圣诞节。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126123637gY2y7CpQsdWoPkfX.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"ujb4\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4309627103475916?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>李宁和国产汽车品牌“红旗”联名推出了“中国制造”系列服饰，</b></a>包括卫衣、帽子等，红旗的汽车元素融入到了服饰设计之中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126122908xZgTOtFyiqYMobSL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126122909lxjfeTUOQYNI50Aq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811261229104tckGBwjpWHRQKPY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126122912wFjzg6dnROJleD5o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126122913CdUerOumfX1giP0o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126122909acimjO6PI7zEnNH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126122910jRyzM8bdOhfiZUp7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811261229117oCh0F8jsRqvUGni.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的Case</h3><p line=\"KWAN\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1687422352/4310545547100687\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>肯德基拍了支“圣诞炸鸡店” 广告，</b></a>由品牌形象代言人周冬雨和鹿晗出演，讨论的还是老话题，坚持梦想还是向现实妥协。肯德基的答案是不如先来吃一桶炸鸡。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=b08024n9i20\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"DvGk\">昨天是国际反家庭暴力日，<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4310160493083931?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>可口可乐办了个名为“不该存在的艺术展”，</b></a> 内涵为话题和展览内容本来是不应该存在的。可口可乐将世界名画化用为遭受家庭暴力的受害者形象，生动展现了家庭暴力的现状。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126123057RFW1LNbZnDgcYqmJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.300000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126123059AKLdcWeO3Zg7DrQ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.300000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126123104B6CpSieZt2l8bYhx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.300000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811261231054m9iLoYjRFtseQAH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.300000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811261231066sD9IUzfXq2eFbyE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.300000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811261231077VbtXP5FNYMW6qaI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.300000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126123105cSehXrkJqb37NHUA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.300000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"TUYZ\">为纪念音乐剧 “Dear Evan Hansen” （致埃文·汉森）演出两周年，潘通为该剧定制发布了<a href=\"https://www.dexigner.com/news/31642\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>“Dear Evan Hansen Blue”</b></a>。该色是看起来充满活力又略带忧郁的浅蓝色，匹配了剧中主人公的情感历程。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126123140P14bnE8CxoAXiSYm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.320313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p line=\"gTLC\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/PqQIr8C0YEwooZk0vGLoDw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>微信封禁了 6000 多个混淆名称的公众号和小程序。</b></a>对于公众号和小程序的名称、logo、简介故意混淆，从而干扰平台搜索结果，或影响用户的识别与判断的行为，平台将对这些内容进行清空或封号处理。</p><p line=\"cw7v\">阿尔法娱乐公司的新商标与 Adidas 著名的三道条纹相近，后者已经和美国专利商标局联系，<b><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/11/25/adidas-wrestles-with-vince-mcmahons-familiar-alpha-entertainment-logo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">希望驳回这一申请</a>。</b><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181126124001vml4cqBQhC80ENT7.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"cw7v\" class=\"\">阿尔法娱乐公司是美国摔跤娱乐公司 WWE 的创始人 Vince McMahon 最近创办的新公司，新公司的项目包括重启之前失败的橄榄球项目 XFL。这一次沿用旧名字，是想建立新的美式足球联盟。</p><p line=\"cw7v\" class=\"\">题图来自：@李宁官方微博</p>"}